text: Het Jignesh Patel (born 13 October 1998) is a Gujarati cricketer.Players at cricketarchive He played 4 matches as a wicket-keeper for India Under-19 in the 2016 Asia cup.2016 Asia Cup Patel was also in the Gujarat squad selected to play against Rest of India for 2016–17 Irani cup but did not made to the playing XI.Gujarat Squad for 2016-17 Irani cup He made his List A debut for Gujarat in the 2016–17 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 25 February 2017. His height is 6'0" (183 cm). == References == Category:1993 births Category:Cricketers from Ahmedabad Category:Living people
